window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Nina</b></p> <p>Charming, captivating, seductive—and a cold-blooded killer. I married the Pakhan of the Russian Bratva anyway. I had to, it was part of the deal.</p> <p>Now, I’m faking marital bliss as I tremble with fear, and I cannot wait to be out of the clutches of this ruthless man.</p> <p><b>Roman</b></p> <p>I get anything I desire, and I want this perfectly imperfect little manipulator. The way she can deceive anyone into believing she’s crazy in love with me just makes me want her even more.</p> <p>She doesn't know it yet, but I am not letting her go.</p> <p>The deal is off.</p>"; 
